<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Reweight final grade calculations</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="b4ebbde5-2fb5-4c12-b2e5-970152eb1fbe" >

    <p>In certain circumstances, it is necessary to re-think the grading of a course. It may be that a semester is cut short, and you suddenly have to re-distribute the weight of assessments that could not be delivered as planned.</p> 
<p>We will explore a few options for rethinking the gradebook, including the reweighting of the grades that factor into the final grade calculation.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#b4ebbde5-2fb5-4c12-b2e5-970152eb1fbe");});</script></div>

				

				
