	<p><strong>Redistribute the weight of the bonus item</strong></p> 
<ul> 
 <li>The weight value of the bonus item will have to be added to another non-bonus graded item.</li> 
 <li><strong>Do not set the weight of the bonus item to 0</strong>, otherwise students won't receive any grades for it!!&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Click <strong>"Save"</strong>, at the bottom of the page, to complete the changes.</p> 
<p><em>In this example, the 5% weight from the (now bonus) "Lab" activity has been added to the "Participation" weight.</em></p>
</div>  
						    
					
